.ie n .IP "$gd = $img\->gd" 4
.el .IP "\f(CW$gd\fR = \f(CW$img\fR\->gd" 4
.IX Item "$gd = $img->gd"
Return the internal GD::Image object.  Usually you will not need to
call this since all \s-1GD\s0 methods are automatically referred to this object.
